  "text": "What is the balance? I am wrong. Imagine if you will the many force fields of the Earth in their geometrically precise web. Energies stream into the earth planes, as you would call them, from magnetically determined points due to growing thought form distortions in understanding of the law of one. The planet itself was seen to have the potential for imbalance. The balancing pyramidal structures were charged with crystals which drew the appropriate balance from the energy forces streaming into the various geometrical centers of electromagnetic energy which surround and shape the planetary sphere.",
